high_descs: Take two steps forward then turn left to face the sink.
Pick up the head of lettuce that's in front of you in the sink.
Turn left and walk to the fridge then turn right to face it.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk past the counter on your left then turn left and walk to the garbage.
Put the head of lettuce in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold head of lettuce in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn left, proceed to refrigerator on right.  Turn right to face refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, place lettuce on shelf to the right of the apple.  Wait four seconds, open door, remove lettuce, close door.
Turn right, proceed to wall, turn left to face wall.  Turn left to face garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Move lettuce from sink to refrigerator, chill, and move lettuce to garbage.

high_descs: Walk to the sink on the left.
Pick up the head of lettuce from inside the sink.
Turn left and walk to the black fridge on the right.
Put the head of lettuce inside the fridge on the bottom shelf to the right of the tomato, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the gray bin on the floor to the left next to the counter.
Put the chilled head of lettuce inside the gray bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce in a bin.
